data.description: This beautiful turnkey 2/2/2 open concept home with cathedral ceilings has a NEWER roof and windows and exterior paint. The kitchen was updated with, appliances and corian countertops and large Tile through out the home. It has an eat in kitchen as well as a dining room. Master bedroom features an ensuite, large walk-in closet. Tall shrubs offer plenty of privacy Model split bedroom home.
